data.title: Mogul Haim Saban Buys 22% of Keshet, Names Two Directors
data.meta_description: After Months of Negotiations, Haim Saban Signed His First Major Deal in Israel Yesterday. The Media Mogul Bought 22 Percent of Channel 2 Franchisee Keshet at an Estimated Price of $2 Million. Of the Three Franchisees, Keshet Is the Most Profitable.
